                  , an <rs id="t17831210-90-viclabel475" type="occupation">infant</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17831210-90-victim985 t17831210-90-viclabel475"></join>, on the King's highway, on the <rs id="t17831210-90-cd476" type="crimeDate">17th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17831210-90-off474 t17831210-90-cd476"></join> last, and putting him in fear, and feloniously taking from his person and against his will, a silk handkerchief, value 2 d. a linen neck-cloth, value 10 d. a pair of stockings, value 6 d. and a linen shirt, value 6 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17831210-90-victim987" type="victimName">
                           Edward 
                           Thompson
                        <interp inst="t17831210-90-victim987" type="surname" value="Thompson"></interp>
