                  <p>
                     <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178312100121"></xptr>THE WHOLE PROCEEDINGS ON THE KING's Commission of the Peace, Oyer and Terminer, and Gaol Delivery for the CITY of LONDON; AND ALSO The Gaol Delivery for the County of Middlesex; HELD AT JUSTICE HALL in the OLD BAILEY, On Wednesday the 10th of DECEMBER, 1783, and the following Days;</p>
                  <p>Being the FIRST SESSION in the Mayoralty of The Right Hon. 
                  <persName id="t17831210-90-person988">
                     ROBERT
                      PECKHAM
                  <interp inst="t17831210-90-person988" type="surname" value="PECKHAM"></interp>
